  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.11">
<l>maṇiyai vāṉavar kaṇṇaṉait taṉṉatō</l>
<l>raṇiyai teṉkuru kūrccaṭa kōpaṉcol</l>
<l>paṇice yāyirat tuḷḷivai pattuṭaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṇivi larkaṟpa rēlkalvi vāyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If those who don’t slacken practice</l>
<l>with these ten among the serving thousand</l>
<l>spoken by Caṭakōpaṉ from southern Kurukūr on the jewel,</l>
<l>on the Kaṇṇaṉ of the celestials [and] on his ornaments,</l>
	<l>[their] erudition will excell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
